1. *Imas* li vremena da se igrame? (Do you have time to play?) 
2. Ona *ima* svoje mišljenje. (She has her own opinion.)
3. Da li *imamo* dovoljno hrane? (Do we have enough food?)
4. Koga *ima*š na fotografiji? (Who is in the photo?) 
5. Zašto *imaš* toliko knjiga? (Why do you have so many books?) 
6. On *ima* oči plave boje. (He has blue eyes.) 
7. Da li *imas* brata? (Do you have a brother?) 
8. Da li *imaju* svi ljudi pravo na obrazovanje? (Do all people have the right to education?)